<body>
    <h1>Ease Anxiety and Mind relaxing Breathing - Guide to Breathing and H=
ow to</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>Use this breathing training technique to ease mind and reduce an=
xiety. It combines calming breathing with a brief pause to activate PNS and=
 to reduce anxiety.</p>
<h2 id=3D"EaseAnxietyandMindrelaxingBreathing-GuidetoBreathingandHowto-Inst=
ructions"><img class=3D"emoticon emoticon-blue-star" data-emoji-id=3D"1f4d8=
" data-emoji-shortname=3D":blue_book:" data-emoji-fallback=3D"\uD83D\uDCD8"=
 src=3D"5b59babcae7cb54d196aaff4825f4bdf56c2bc39e071c1fbc3297ad49d2560f7" w=
idth=3D"16" height=3D"16" data-emoticon-name=3D"blue-star" alt=3D"(blue sta=
r)">&nbsp;Instructions</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Find a comfortable seated position.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Use a 60BPM metronome as the guide. Each tik sound of the metronome repr=
esents one second / one count.</p></li>
<li>
<p>&nbsp;You can use this metronome link <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D=
"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3DymJIXzvDvj4" rel=3D"nofollow">60 BPM - M=
etronome - YouTube</a></p></li>
<li>
<p>Inhale deeply through your nose for a count of 4.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hold your breath for a count of 1.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Exhale slowly and completely through your mouth for a count of 6.</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>Pause for a count of 1 before beginning the next inhale.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Repeat this pattern, maintaining a relaxed pace.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Practice breathing for 4-5 mins for optimum benefit</p></li>
<li>
<p>If it feels difficult to continue this pattern for more than 2-3 minutes=
, take a short break and start gain. Continue till you feel your less anxio=
us.</p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p><strong>Biofeedback:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Focus on the pause after exhaling, letting go of any tension.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Feel anxiety melting away with each exhale.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Experience a sense of relief and ease.</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
